reviewText: Excellent dvd's hope there will be more.
This is a movie the whole family can watch together.  I love Cantinflas.
I thought the quality of the DVD would be significantly better.  It was kind of dark throughout the entire movie and the DVD seem to "skip" a couple of times.

Maybe his best film.  Mario Moreno is a genius.  Should be remastered with multi-lingual captions.
In my humble opinion, I think this is one of Cantiflas greatest movies.  Fun for the entire family. Teaches great lesson as well. It looks great for such an old movie.
With Cantinflas you can never go wrong. Hilarious comedy.
